    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="写作"><a href="#写作" class="headerlink" title="写作"></a>写作</h1><h3 id="new"><a href="#new" class="headerlink" title="new"></a>new</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new [layout] &lt;title&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">layout：</span><br><span class="line">hexo有三种默认布局，不同布局的文件会被放在不同的文件夹下</span><br><span class="line">布局路径</span><br><span class="line">    postsource/_posts</span><br><span class="line">    pagesource</span><br><span class="line">    draftsource/_drafts</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="上传笔记到git"><a href="#上传笔记到git" class="headerlink" title="上传笔记到git"></a>上传笔记到git</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">配置git用户名和邮箱</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.name &quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email &quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">配置ssh</span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;they_know@163.com&quot;</span><br><span class="line">输入存放路径</span><br><span class="line">输入密码</span><br><span class="line">再次输入密码</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">将.pub秘钥添加到github设置中即可</span><br><span class="line">部署网页</span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy(简写hexo d)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="主题"><a href="#主题" class="headerlink" title="主题"></a>主题</h1><p>下载主题到themes目录下</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/MOxFIVE/hexo-theme-yelee themes/yelee</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更改_config.yml文件中的theme值</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">theme: yelee</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="插件"><a href="#插件" class="headerlink" title="插件"></a>插件</h1>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
